  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting social inclusion and fighting terrorism</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The recent terrorist attacks in Paris remind us how important it is to promote tolerance and fight obscurantism. One of the root causes of such acts of violence is social exclusion in underpriviledged neighborhoods. Education is a powerful leverage for social change.  Today, PL4Y International intends to launch a sport based project to help children learn tolerance, empathy and develop life skills in 10 districts in the Paris region where poverty and social exclusion is strong.</narrative>
  </description>
